      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "CoordinatorAgent (orchestrator)\n    |\n    +-- UniverseAgent -> Universe.py\n    |   (stock selection)\n    |\n    +-- AlphaAgent -> Alpha.py\n    |   (signal generation)\n    |\n    +-- RiskAgent -> Risk.py\n    |   (risk management)\n    |\n    +-- StrategyAgent -> Main.py\n        (integration)",
