      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "SELF-IMPROVEMENT LOOP:\n\n  +---> [1] _fetch_papers() --> CrossRef API + NLP Pipeline\n  |           |\n  |           v\n  |     [2] _generate_strategy() --> CoordinatorAgent\n  |           |\n  |           v\n  |     [3] _validate_and_learn() --> ErrorLearner\n  |           |                       (analyze + fix errors)\n  |           v\n  |     [4] _backtest() --> QuantConnect MCP\n  |           |\n  |           v\n  |     [5] PerformanceLearner --> analyze results\n  |           |                    (success/failure patterns)\n  |           v\n  +-----[6] PromptRefiner --> inject learnings into next iteration",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "SELF-IMPROVEMENT LOOP:\n\n  +---> [1] _fetch_papers() --> CrossRef API + NLP Pipeline\n  |           |\n  |           v\n  |     [2] _generate_strategy() --> CoordinatorAgent\n  |           |\n  |           v\n  |     [3] _validate_and_learn() --> ErrorLearner\n  |           |                       (analyze + fix errors)\n  |           v\n  |     [4] _backtest() --> QuantConnect MCP\n  |           |\n  |           v\n  |     [5] PerformanceLearner --> analyze results\n  |           |                    (success/failure patterns)\n  |           v\n  +-----[6] PromptRefiner --> inject learnings into next iteration",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
