      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "ErrorLearner (learner.py):\n  - Classify errors (import, name, syntax, API)\n  - Store error->fix mappings\n  - Self-healing with learned fixes\n\nPerformanceLearner (learner.py):\n  - Analyze poor performance (low Sharpe, high DD)\n  - Identify success patterns\n  - Generate recommendations\n\nPromptRefiner (prompt_refiner.py):\n  - Inject learnings into agent prompts\n  - Include error avoidance patterns\n  - Add success patterns from top strategies",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "ErrorLearner (learner.py):\n  - Classify errors (import, name, syntax, API)\n  - Store error->fix mappings\n  - Self-healing with learned fixes\n\nPerformanceLearner (learner.py):\n  - Analyze poor performance (low Sharpe, high DD)\n  - Identify success patterns\n  - Generate recommendations\n\nPromptRefiner (prompt_refiner.py):\n  - Inject learnings into agent prompts\n  - Include error avoidance patterns\n  - Add success patterns from top strategies",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
